- app.py
  The main backend Python file containing the web application logic using a web framework (e.g., Flask). It handles routing, page rendering, data processing, and file I/O operations for all pages and functionalities described in the requirements.

- templates/
  Directory containing HTML template files for each of the nine pages defined in the requirements. These templates include the specified elements with their IDs and structure, and are rendered dynamically by app.py.

